    Risorsa     URL da Windows                              Serve SSH tunnel?
    ---------   -----------------------------------------   --------------------
    Rancher A   https://localhost:8443/login                Si' (8443) + port-fwd
    Rancher B   https://rancher.app.iac-svil.almaviva.it    No (DNS + Internal LB)
    Dashboard   http://localhost:8080/#/dashboard           Si' (8080)
